description: This header file defines a mock class 'CloudStoreImplementationMock' for testing purposes. The class inherits from multiple interfaces related to cloud storage management, including store, store2, store cache, store inspector, and store limit. It uses Google Mock to mock various methods for testing interactions with cloud storage functionalities.
